Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:03.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the powers of the Soul Reaper\Nwere thrust upon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:05.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my whole world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:07.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Substitute Soul Reaper,\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:11.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wield this sword\Nwith all of my soul and strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.68,0:00:14.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to protect my precious friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:25.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:31.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one can take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:36.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never fade, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:49.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun never blinds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:54.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a flower that blooms in shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:01:04.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Exhale those feelings you hold inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:14.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only;\Nnow and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:25.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The day may come\Nwhen all will rise against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:30.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:34.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never give up, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:40.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,TIME NOTICE THAT\NYOU SHOULD NOTICE THAT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:44.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,NOTICE THAT THERE’S NO OTHER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:56.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time\Nyou're seeing this, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:02:00.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fighting technique that\Ncombines Hakuda and Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's something I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:05.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should feel privileged.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:08.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This technique has only\Nbeen completed recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:11.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so you're the first person\NI'm going to test it on in a real fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:14.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't even have a name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:16.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:19.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It has a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:21.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:25.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's called, Shunko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:50.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. I really didn't want to fight\Nyou with this technique…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Soi Fon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:03:01.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can't control\Nthis technique very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:21.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:27.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,why I never showed you\Nthis technique until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's because this technique\Nis too dangerous…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:52.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early for you\Nto use this technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Hankisosai…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:58.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You cancel the opponent's Kido\Nby crushing it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:01.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with Kido of the same quality\Nand strength but with opposite spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:06.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But she did it so quickly and effortlessly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,against this much speed\Nand pressure of my Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:11.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stronger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m supposed to have already…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,surpassed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:25.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A century of isolation should have made\Nyou weaker and me stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:30.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you still standing\Nin front of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:34.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still dominating me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see her, Shaolin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:48.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The one on the palanquin is\Nthe princess of the Shihoin Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the appointed Tenshiheisoban,\NDefender of the Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:54.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She will one day lead\Nthe Punishment Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:59.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We the Fon Clan,\Ndevote everything to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:03.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:08.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is our duty and fate,\Nand yours as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:13.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From this day on,\Nyour name will be Soi Fon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and you will live only to serve her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:23.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I met her,\Nit was like meeting a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Fon clan is\Na low-ranking noble house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:31.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the generations, we made\Nour living as executioners and assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:34.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Strength is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:37.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those who cannot even make it\Ninto the Punishment Force
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,are disowned from the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:41.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:49.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you stand out like that,\Nyou woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:06.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become stronger.\NStronger than anyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Force Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You there, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:35.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,M-My name is Soi Fon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:44.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I adored her…immensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:49.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was beyond adoration.\NI worshipped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, seven years after\NI joined the Force came the day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:56.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was named to the Commander’s\NPersonal Guard Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:00.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soi Fon at your service,\NYour Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:04.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you've come!\NYou heard about it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! From this day on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:10.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will sacrifice my body and soul\Nto protect Your Excelle--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s too formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop with the “Your Excellency” stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:18.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can address me with\Nsomething simple, like “Ms. Yoruichi.”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:21.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:23.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I could never do that to\NYour Excellency…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:36.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then…would it be all right if\NI call you Lady Yoruichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are so uptight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. Call me whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:47.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted you here because\NI'm confident in your skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what you call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:53.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm expecting you to do well\Nat your post, Soi Fon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:59.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You will live only to serve her…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:01.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:06.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will live only to serve Lady Yoruichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I had no hesitation…\NI was happy…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Soi Fon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:22.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting used to\Nthe duties in the Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:24.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, Your Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:30.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Buzz buzz.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Buzz buzz buzz--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:33.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:35.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a small bee here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:41.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you\Nto call me "Yoruichi."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:46.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,B-But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:47.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lady…Yoruichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:54.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:56.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:57.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:08:59.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:05.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I tell you to come, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:07.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:12.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:14.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:21.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:57.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy even in\Nthe middle of battle…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's pull out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:07.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to protect you,\Nyet I wasn't strong enough…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:13.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:16.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I say it's okay, then it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your Exce--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:26.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, thank you very much…\NLady Yoruichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:28.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:29.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:38.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't protect Lady Yoruichi\Nbeing like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:42.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:49.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:52.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soi Fon, this is how you swing a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You step in…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:13.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think too hard.\NYou're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I’m not good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:22.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect you, Lady Yoruichi,\NI need more power…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:25.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm lacking in everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:31.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Yoruichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:37.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:42.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes feel like\Nyou're my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:47.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like me is undeserving\Nof such words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:55.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said that's enough.\NIt's a full moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will always be by your side\Nto protect you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forever…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:28.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:37.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy. Until that day…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:01.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It happened so suddenly…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:12.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You disappeared without\Nany words of farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:21.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was a betrayal of my master\Nwho I adored like a goddess…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:23.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Liar…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was disappointed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hated you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:31.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And even cursed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:34.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I vowed that I would become\Nstronger than you…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:38.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and catch you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:47.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you for betraying\Nmy devotion and trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:48.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:10.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:19.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you not take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Yoruichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:37.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten stronger since\Nthe last time I saw you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:55.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was some wild lightning\Njust now, wasn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:15:00.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we had our swords up in the air,\Nit would’ve struck us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:05.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! That's no ordinary lightning.\NThat's Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:09.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's fired at specific targets.\NIt won't come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:16.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sure haven’t gotten\Nany better, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:18.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:24.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kido is just not my thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:31.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a versatile type of person\Nwho’s born with the Zan Ken So Ki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:36.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't always as versatile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:40.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re more likely to be appointed\Nlieutenant if you're versatile,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,rather than excelling in\Njust one skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:46.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I became versatile to\Nbecome a lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound like much fun…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:57.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! A man should always strive\Nto rise through the ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it’s fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:01.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's for your mother, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:05.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:10.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who’d aim to become a lieutenant\Nfor that old hag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:12.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The sake is all gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:16.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:19.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You drink too much at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:23.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy. It’s only natural\Nthat sake should disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s because you drank it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:28.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make it sound like it\Njust evaporated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:31.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. Then let's do the next round!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:32.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:40.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And again! And again!\NAnd again! And again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:46.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m taking the high ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Again?! That’s not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:52.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! It's your fault that you're weak\Nat rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:01.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:06.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who's fighting with Captain Kuchiki\Nup at the Sokyoku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:08.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not familiar with\Nthat Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:11.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s the Ryoka, the Ryoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:17.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know because I fought him once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:19.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… A Ryoka, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:23.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This Ryoka is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take your stance, Iba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:28.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:30.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The loser has to go get more sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The winner gets to take a break\Nin the meanwhile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:40.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you hold back…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:41.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:16.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You've mastered the Flash Step.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:17.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How leisurely. As always.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:24.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be casually\Nanalyzing my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But is that what you should be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:34.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't even put\Na scratch on me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:39.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you telling me that\Nthis is all you’ve got?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:44.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:49.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that you were going\Nto cut me down
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:52.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and execute Rukia yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:19:01.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat you…\Nwith everything I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:06.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to crush all of your powers\Nuntil there's nothing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:10.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You said you're going to\Nexecute your own sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:17.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about your reasons\Nor position!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I will never let you say\Nsuch a thing in front of Rukia again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Release your Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:30.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A cheap provocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:34.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can holler all you want,\Nbut I will not change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:39.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It will not change Rukia’s fate,\Nnor your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get full of yourself, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:50.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a thousand years too early\Nfor the likes of you to die by my Bankai…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Senbonzakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:41.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the power of your zanpakuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:45.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I swing my sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:51.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my zanpakuto absorbs\Nmy Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:54.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then it releases highly concentrated\NSpiritual Pressure from its blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:58.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nit casts an amplified swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's Zangetsu's ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:05.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was never able to aim at anything\Nwith this shot before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:11.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even know how\Nto fire it until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:15.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke Urahara told me…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:22.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I can only teach you the stances.”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:27.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I finally know what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:33.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zangetsu was the only one who\Ncould teach me about Zangetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:39.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At last you are able to fire\Na shot at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall tell you, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:45.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is a big difference in its power
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:50.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when you know its name\Nthan when you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:53.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this well, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:55.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The name of that attack is…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:01.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:05.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:08.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.17,0:22:15.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me with your Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:19.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:31.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All the days gone by\Nhave made me what I am
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:37.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Life’s not easy;\Nthat’s why I can go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:52.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people hurrying by,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:56.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“Have your dreams come true?”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:23:01.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m still struggling…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:11.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forget returning to my youth;\NI want to live today well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:16.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was born timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:25.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Out where the sun shines\NI fisted my hand tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:32.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Break out of that place, that time,\Nand I can change my life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:40.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I could never express\Neverything deep in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:46.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Life’s not easy;\Nthat’s why I can go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.17,0:23:57.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Now that the fight between\Nthe women is decided,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we'll show you a fight between\Nsome cool guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:01.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Iba!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:02.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:03.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt while\Nyou were getting all excited,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:06.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but we don't want to see\Nyour unbearably grungy battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:07.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so we're moving on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:08.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:08.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.85,0:24:10.85,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu's Super Heartfelt Diary
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.29,0:24:15.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother finally came home\Nfrom his trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.76,0:24:18.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there’s something strange\Nabout him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:22.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He seems afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.24,0:24:27.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And did he look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.43,0:24:31.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he has something\Non his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.72,0:24:34.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.51,0:24:39.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bostov!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.89,0:24:48.82,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tune in again!